35:44.021 --> 35:45.438
It's OK, I'm buying.

35:45.565 --> 35:47.399
And I'm eating.

35:53.072 --> 35:56.741
That was nice of Dexter
to let you out early tonight.

35:57.076 --> 35:59.286
Yeah, he's such a good boss.

35:59.912 --> 36:03.081
He works around my school schedule,
whatever I need.

36:03.249 --> 36:04.749
He's a good guy.

36:05.084 --> 36:08.420
With all he went through last year,
you know, losing his wife...

36:08.546 --> 36:09.963
I'm glad he's got you helping him out.

36:10.298 --> 36:12.299
Yeah, so sad.

36:12.717 --> 36:14.885
Well, I think he's putting it
all behind him at least.

36:15.928 --> 36:17.971
Well, I don't know. Some nights...

36:18.973 --> 36:20.265
What?

36:20.892 --> 36:24.477
It just seems like some nights,
the pain, the loneliness,

36:24.604 --> 36:26.771
whatever it is he's feeling,
gets to be too much

36:26.814 --> 36:29.232
and he's gotta
just disappear for a while,

36:29.442 --> 36:31.234
go out on his boat.

36:31.611 --> 36:33.445
I think he's trying
to keep it away from Harrison.

36:33.571 --> 36:35.614
Yeah. He really loves his son.

36:36.490 --> 36:37.616
Poor guy needs a hobby or something.

36:38.075 --> 36:39.451
Totally. Thank you.

36:39.619 --> 36:42.996
Thanks. Can I get a nice
bottle of champagne, please?

36:43.164 --> 36:44.456
Thanks.

36:44.916 --> 36:47.959
Champagne? What is up with you?

36:48.336 --> 36:50.170
We're celebrating.

36:50.713 --> 36:52.797
You're looking at
the next lieutenant of Homicide.

36:53.049 --> 36:55.634
You? Angel!

36:55.676 --> 36:57.344
That is so fantastic!

36:57.470 --> 36:59.512
- Wait, when did this happen?
- It's not official yet.

36:59.639 --> 37:01.723
I'm only acting LT, but, you know,

37:01.807 --> 37:03.350
it should come through any day now.

37:03.476 --> 37:04.809
I am so happy for you.

37:04.894 --> 37:06.186
It comes with a nice salary bump.

37:06.312 --> 37:08.647
We can finally get out
of that little apartment

37:08.689 --> 37:11.191
- and into a nice house.
- Wouldn't that be so great?

37:11.400 --> 37:13.652
I could put Auri
back in ballet lessons.

37:13.736 --> 37:15.237
How's she doing?

37:15.404 --> 37:17.405
You know, a teenager.

37:18.407 --> 37:20.659
She doesn't need her daddy any more.

37:21.035 --> 37:22.911
It's a phase, I'm sure.

37:22.995 --> 37:24.412
I'm sure.

37:25.539 --> 37:26.998
