37:53.067 --> 37:54.442
Because you just took off your top.

37:54.527 --> 37:56.945
- You're all sexualised.
- Oh, my God!

37:57.405 --> 37:59.030
You're serious!

37:59.365 --> 38:01.032
I know we didn't grow up together,

38:01.075 --> 38:03.868
- but I'm your sister, Angel.
