Some lady called it in.

40:35.938 --> 40:37.230
He's dead.

40:37.356 --> 40:38.440
That's your best guy?

40:39.900 --> 40:41.234
Looks like he was killed
by the stab wound.

40:41.360 --> 40:42.777
He wasn't drowned.

40:42.862 --> 40:44.612
His body was put
in the water postmortem.

40:45.114 --> 40:47.073
So he was dumped.
Someone tried to hide the body?

40:48.117 --> 40:49.367
Vince?

40:49.452 --> 40:51.244
He wasn't in the water very long.

40:51.370 --> 40:52.871
Three, four hours, max.

40:52.955 --> 40:54.122
So he was dumped right offshore.

40:54.415 --> 40:56.332
Doesn't look like somebody
was trying to hide him.

40:56.625 --> 40:58.793
No, more like they wanted
the body to be found.

40:58.878 --> 41:01.129
Last thing I need
is a complicated crime scene.

41:02.298 --> 41:03.840
Holy shit.

41:04.175 --> 41:06.301
Someone cut him open,
then sewed him back up.

41:06.677 --> 41:08.136
And it just got complicated.

41:08.554 --> 41:10.305
These incisions were made postmortem.

41:11.056 --> 41:12.849
Our fruit vendor?

41:18.147 --> 41:20.190
- Omar Rivera.
- That's our guy.

41:23.652 --> 41:25.153
These stitchings are really weird.

41:25.279 --> 41:27.655
There's, like, an "A" and
then a horseshoe kind of thing.

41:29.366 --> 41:31.576
It's Greek. Alpha, omega.

41:31.952 --> 41:33.411
How do you know Greek?

41:33.537 --> 41:35.371
I dated some sorority chicks
back in the day.

41:35.915 --> 41:37.081
Of course you did.

41:40.753 --> 41:42.086
Holy shit, it's moving.

41:42.379 --> 41:43.505
There's something inside.

41:53.349 --> 41:55.558
Holy frankenfuck! Snakes!

42:00.648 --> 42:01.773
Bag 'em, bag 'em.

42:19.875 --> 42:20.959
- Got 'em all?
- Yeah.

42:21.043 --> 42:23.086
- How many we got?
- Seven.

42:24.255 --> 42:25.505
Seven snakes.

42:29.009 --> 42:30.301
Your guy just fainted.

42:31.929 --> 42:34.097
That's not a good sign
for a crime scene investigator.

42:34.557 --> 42:36.349
Goodbye, big guy.

42:36.433 --> 42:38.309
Hello, runner-up, little Miss Hottie.

42:38.394 --> 42:39.978
Can we get back to this, please?

42:40.187 --> 42:41.813
Snakes. I mean, what the fuck?

42:42.439 --> 42:45.400
How does that happen? I mean, what?
Did the snakes crawl inside of him?

42:46.110 --> 42:48.027
No, they're freshwater snakes.
Somebody put them there.

42:48.153 --> 42:50.613
Somebody cut him open,
took out his intestines,

42:50.698 --> 42:52.490
and replaced them with snakes.

42:52.700 --> 42:55.159
- Why?
- To send a message, maybe?

42:58.122 --> 42:59.956
Dude, what kind of message
does it send

43:00.040 --> 43:01.666
putting snakes
in a dead guy's stomach?

43:02.167 --> 43:03.835
Some kind of warning, maybe.

43:05.879 --> 43:07.630
Whatever the message, whoever sent it

43:07.715 --> 43:09.424
went to a lot of time and trouble.

43:10.342 --> 43:12.135
This is no amateur.

43:24.523 --> 43:25.773
After Joe's had a couple of drinks,

43:25.899 --> 43:27.900
I'll figure out a way
to get him to step outside,

43:27.985 --> 43:30.153
- where I'll M99 him and...
- Dexter!

43:31.989 --> 43:33.323
Trisha.

43:33.449 --> 43:34.532
- Hi.
- Hi.

43:35.367 --> 43:37.619
I was hoping I'd see you
before the weekend was over.

43:38.203 --> 43:40.121
Oh, well, here I am.

43:42.958 --> 43:44.083
Shall we?

43:45.127 --> 43:48.087
If it wasn't for you, I'd have never
made it through high school.

43:53.385 --> 43:55.219
You saved my life.

43:56.138 --> 43:58.139
I saved your... How?

43:59.350 --> 44:00.892
We had so many classes together,

44:00.976 --> 44:02.685
and I'd always sit right behind you.

44:02.853 --> 44:05.563
Every test we took,
I'd copy all your answers.

44:05.731 --> 44:08.441
- It's how I got through.
- Oh, well, I never noticed.

44:09.276 --> 44:11.736
That's OK. That makes us even.

44:12.738 --> 44:14.447
I never noticed how cute you are.

44:15.074 --> 44:16.699
Until now.

44:19.370 --> 44:22.163
Oh, my God, Mr Smith's class.

44:22.247 --> 44:23.956
This is it.

44:25.417 --> 44:27.210
You helped me a lot in this classroom.

44:36.512 --> 44:38.513
Maybe I should give you
a little something back.

44:41.975 --> 44:43.559
Trisha, I don't have time for this.

44:43.644 --> 44:45.228
Yes, you do.

44:52.736 --> 44:56.155
This is really...

44:57.449 --> 44:59.033
Stop talking, Dexter.

45:19.263 --> 45:22.181
Oh, God, what did I get myself into?

45:22.307 --> 45:24.100
This is never good.

45:25.352 --> 45:27.186
That was so good.

45:27.312 --> 45:28.980
Thanks, sweetie.

45:41.118 --> 45:42.618
Your purse.

45:44.371 --> 45:46.497
- Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

45:47.166 --> 45:49.083
Whoa, that was easy.

46:07.728 --> 46:10.646
Trisha, you bad girl.

46:38.008 --> 46:39.675
What is this?

46:40.928 --> 46:42.178
Trisha?

46:43.806 --> 46:45.139
You here?

46:45.474 --> 46:47.642
What the fuck?

46:47.768 --> 46:49.977
Fast reflexes. I hate jocks.

46:50.479 --> 46:53.773
- It's you.
- I'm a mighty panther.

46:58.237 --> 47:00.112
I'm the gold and red.

47:00.489 --> 47:02.406
Jesus, you still are some weird loser.

47:02.783 --> 47:03.950
What the fuck's up with you?

47:04.284 --> 47:05.952
Tonight is meant for victory.

47:06.036 --> 47:08.204
It's time to make you dead.

47:10.290 --> 47:11.833
I don't think that last line is right.

47:11.959 --> 47:13.251
I'm pretty sure it is.

47:32.062 --> 47:33.729
Welcome back.

47:34.815 --> 47:36.274
What the hell is going on?

47:36.733 --> 47:38.734
Why'd you do it, Joe?

47:40.612 --> 47:42.488
- Why'd you kill Janet?
- What?

47:42.865 --> 47:45.074
Who said I killed Janet?
I didn't kill Janet. I was...

47:46.910 --> 47:47.952
No more lies.

47:52.416 --> 47:55.626
I'm a blood spatter expert, remember?
I see things others miss.

47:58.463 --> 48:01.048
You shot Janet,
then put the gun in her hand.

48:01.258 --> 48:03.843
No, I came home and I found her...

48:03.927 --> 48:06.679
OK, OK, OK.

48:06.889 --> 48:08.055
But I had to.

48:08.140 --> 48:09.765
Yeah? Why? Why'd you have to?

48:10.517 --> 48:13.978
Because we were having problems,
and the marriage was over.

48:14.062 --> 48:16.731
- And...
- And so you killed her?

48:17.941 --> 48:19.525
Do you know
how expensive a divorce is?

48:19.818 --> 48:21.152
Really?

48:21.403 --> 48:23.195
That's your answer?

48:31.622 --> 48:33.789
What would Jesus have done?

48:35.542 --> 48:37.251
Seriously now.

48:43.884 --> 48:46.385
How do you reconcile your belief
in a higher power, in a god,

48:46.470 --> 48:47.511
with what you've done?

48:48.847 --> 48:50.097
What difference does it make?

48:50.223 --> 48:51.641
I'm just curious.

48:51.850 --> 48:54.560
So what, I'm supposed
to defend my beliefs to you?

48:55.395 --> 48:57.229
If you don't mind.

48:57.648 --> 49:00.942
Look, I mean, everyone makes mistakes.

49:03.153 --> 49:05.196
And they do things
that they shouldn't do.

49:05.280 --> 49:08.783
And they're only human.
But God, see, God forgives us.

49:08.867 --> 49:10.451
Really, it's as simple as that?

49:10.535 --> 49:12.244
You kill someone,
God forgives you for it?

49:12.329 --> 49:13.579
- Yes.
- So I could kill you

49:13.664 --> 49:15.039
- and God would forgive me?
- Well, no.

49:15.123 --> 49:17.249
- You just said he would.
- You have to truly repent.

49:19.670 --> 49:21.754
Do you truly repent for killing Janet?

49:21.838 --> 49:23.714
- Yes, definitely.
- Liar.

49:23.799 --> 49:25.341
No, no, you don't wanna do that!

49:26.259 --> 49:27.802
- Why is that?
- Cos...

49:28.428 --> 49:30.513
If you let me go,
God will give you life everlasting

49:30.597 --> 49:32.848
and whatever you want.

49:32.933 --> 49:34.767
There's really nothing I need.

49:36.687 --> 49:38.771
You know, you don't wanna...

49:38.855 --> 49:40.523
You don't wanna make God mad.

49:41.066 --> 49:42.650
Don't you hear how foolish you sound?

49:42.734 --> 49:44.318
Because he will smite you

49:44.444 --> 49:46.779
with swords and rocks and thunder.

49:46.905 --> 49:50.116
Thunder is just the noise.
It would be lightning.

49:50.200 --> 49:52.576
You cannot kill me,
for God is a mighty fortress.

49:52.661 --> 49:53.703
Joe, please, stop.

49:53.870 --> 49:56.998
And I have been washed with the blood
of the lamb and he will protect me!

50:02.295 --> 50:04.296
Sorry, hammer time.

50:09.469 --> 50:11.178
So I talked to the coast guard today,

50:11.263 --> 50:13.180
and they confirmed
what we'd already figured.

50:13.557 --> 50:15.558
With the tides and all that,
that body was probably

50:15.642 --> 50:18.269
tossed in the water
no more than a 1/4 mile offshore.

50:20.439 --> 50:21.772
Really?

50:21.898 --> 50:23.441
You don't seem very interested.

50:23.525 --> 50:26.569
No, of course I'm interested.
I just...

50:28.155 --> 50:29.488
Don't really wanna talk about work.

50:29.573 --> 50:31.699
What is going on with you?
You're acting so weird lately.

50:31.783 --> 50:33.075
I'm not acting weird, I...

50:33.160 --> 50:34.702
You're about to drink the candle.

50:38.331 --> 50:40.291
I'm just gonna use the restroom.

50:52.137 --> 50:53.429
Debra...

50:54.931 --> 50:56.807
will you marry me?

50:58.351 --> 50:59.810
God, I sound like a fucking idiot.

51:02.981 --> 51:04.482
Thank you.

51:07.277 --> 51:09.070
Get down, get down, get down!

51:18.080 --> 51:19.497
Fuck! He's wearing Kevlar.

51:32.052 --> 51:33.552
Don't fuckin' move!

51:34.554 --> 51:35.679
You all right?

51:35.764 --> 51:37.139
Yeah.

51:42.270 --> 51:43.979
Life is good.

51:45.190 --> 51:46.857
I'm not at all unhappy.

51:46.942 --> 51:50.861
I'm quite content to go about my life
believing in nothing,

51:51.571 --> 51:54.240
with no fear that there might be
something more out there.

51:58.161 --> 52:00.579
"I stood upon the sand of the sea,

52:01.540 --> 52:04.083
"and I saw a serpent
rise up out of the sea,

52:04.459 --> 52:06.293
"having seven heads."

52:06.962 --> 52:09.630
"And upon his heads,
the name of blasphemy."

52:13.385 --> 52:14.802
So it's begun?

52:14.886 --> 52:18.180
Yes. It's begun.

52:24.896 --> 52:26.689
But I also have a son,

52:26.773 --> 52:28.440
and I have to think
about what he wants

52:28.525 --> 52:30.109
and what's best for him,

52:30.193 --> 52:31.944
because who knows?

52:32.112 --> 52:34.655
Maybe he'll grow up to be someone
who wants to think about

52:35.365 --> 52:36.740
those kinds of things.
